<br>
<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>There are exactly 7 days reserved by Guilds for the month of August. There are 24 other days when muliple groups of people can go up and camp to their hearts content. Why would/does anyone want to/have to go on a day that's reserved?<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
